name: SwellSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open swell sounds”
”Alexa ask swell sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: swell sounds
des: A big swell is raging deep in the ocean. Listen to the relaxing sounds as the waves wash upon the shore! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Swell Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
